.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
5 different games are played: whist, bridge, backgammon, go, billiard
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
City: nizza, hannover, london, colone, boston
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the english is the person playing whist
2. the spanish is the owner of the dog
3. the person drinking coffee is the person playing bridge
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person playing bridge is to the right of the person playing backgammon
6. the person traveling to nizza is the owner of the snails
7. the person traveling to hannover is the person playing go
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person traveling to hannover is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person traveling to boston
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person playing billiard

.:: Answer ::.
